@Node "SILENCE" "AmIRC.guide/SILENCE"
@Toc "Commands"

Commands
========

SILENCE
-------

Usage: @{b}/SILENCE [[+|-]nick|userhost]@{ub}

Explanation of SILENCE.

EXAMPLES:

@{b}/SILENCE@{ub}

